<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7db19dc1cd7745cca70c05f9b2dcbe8b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 华为儿童帐号的“家庭群组”功能</p>
